For the time being, I've delayed collection of logs from my NetApp devices instead of rolling back. TextBody:
Not a problem at all.

Main reason I was reaching out was because I was wondering if you had tried any uninstall type tool to remove whatever is causing problems with this proxy installer?

Fix problems that block programs from being installed or removed - Microsoft Support

This is a pretty handy tool that you can snag and Run to attempt to fully remove either the 11.6 or 12.0 proxy, not sure which will show up on the list.

Then you could attempt a reinstall of 12.0.

If you'd like a meeting to go over or run through this let me know and I'll shoot out an invite.

Thanks,

msiexec /i auditor-enterprise-FileSystemProxy-12.0.0.1030.msi LICENSE_FILE=C:UsersusernameStealthAUDIT.LIC
